description:
Mcpc:  Table storing Ericsson-specific attributes of  Multiple Cell Power Control (MCPC) measurements for specific cells in a given area at a particular time.

dateTime: Timestamp of the MCPC measurement.
Area_Name: Name of the geographic area where the measurement was taken.
CellId: Unique identifier of the cell site.
Id2: Redundant/Duplicate of CellId.
Id3:  Likely an unnecessary or placeholder identifier (value consistently '1').
vsDataType: Specifies the data type as MCPC data.
vsDataFormatVersion: Specifies the version of the Ericsson-specific MCPC data format.
Mcpc.mcpcId:  Identifier for the specific MCPC measurement instance.
